lead_paragraph: Rougned Odor followed his game-ending shot Tuesday night with two more homers Wednesday, and the Texas Rangers completed a sweep of the Seattle Mariners.

headline.print_headline: Odor Homers Twice, Gomez Hits Slam as Rangers Rout Mariners
